# Shared Contracts

Domain DTOs and contracts used across services.

## Conventions
- Pydantic for Python; TypeScript interfaces for frontend
- Shared job DTO, workflow DTO, application DTO
- Status enums: workflow, task, application, fetch run
- Event payload schemas for inter-service communication

## Rules
- Contracts defined before feature implementation
- No service-specific logic in shared modules
